# Mini CompanyOS AI

Multi-agent AI decision platform for business leaders.

## Features
- 3 specialized agents (Sales, Finance, HR) running in parallel
- CEO agent that synthesizes all reports into a final decision
- Hindsight memory — remembers past decisions across sessions
- CascadeFlow model routing — smart model selection per task

## Live Demo
[Click here to try it](https://YOUR_USERNAME.github.io/mini-companyos-ai/mini_companyos_ai.html)

